1. Fetch Weather from NOAA/ Severity
2. write the data to file, store.txt constantly every 5 minutes in case power goes out
3. if online than use IBM llm to inform the user of current weather and what to do
4. Text to speech the audio for user.
5. Take user input from express to send ask questions
6. if offline use local ollama model to help the user.


